ac.ucy.cs.spdx.graph

Class LicenseNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • ac.ucy.cs.spdx.graph.LicenseNode

  • public class LicenseNode
extends java.lang.Object
    This is License Node class. It is the representation of vertices in the licenseGraph as seen in /resources/LicenseCompatGraph.png. It consists of several useful methods for creating the nodes and accessing data of them.
    Author:
    dpasch01
